**Example 1: 下载合同**

下载合同

Input: 

```
tccli ds DownloadContract --cli-unfold-argument  \
    --Module ContractMng \
    --Operation DownloadContract \
    --ContractResId dcc-480rzey2ww
```

Output: 
```
{
    "Response": {
        "RequestId": "7896ed76-c159-4b71-9fc4-c445c9c113c4",
        "TaskId": 2
    }
}
```
